       <span id="ctl00_pageContent_breadCrumbs"><a target="_self" href="/Content.aspx?id=12375" title="<p>Circulation Policy Eligible Borrowers The facilities and collections of Preston Library are primarily for the use of the VMI Corps of Cadets, faculty and staff, but visitors are always welcome. Circulation privileges are extended to the faculty and students of</p>">Circulation Policy</a></span> 
      </div> 
      <div id="ctl00_pageContent_sectionbanner" class="section-banner" data-set="banner"> 
       <div class="append-wrap"> 
        <div id="sectionBranding"> 
